# 📘 Case 03 - Sorting Data

## 🎯 Objective
Learn how to sort Excel data ascending/descending using UiPath.

---

## 📝 Sample Data
(same as previous cases)

---

## 🛠️ Steps
1. Read `Students.xlsx` into `dtStudents`
2. Use **Sort Data Table** → Column: `Score`, Order: Descending
3. Write sorted data into `Sorted.xlsx`

---

## ✅ Expected Output
| ID  | Name    | Score |
|-----|---------|-------|
| 8   | Hannah  | 92    |
| 3   | Charlie | 90    |
| 6   | Fiona   | 88    |
| 1   | Alice   | 85    |
| 10  | Julia   | 80    |
| 5   | Ethan   | 75    |
| 2   | Bob     | 70    |
| 9   | Ian     | 65    |
| 4   | Diana   | 60    |
| 7   | George  | 55    |

---

## 📦 Covered Activities
- `Sort Data Table`
